Name: NodeAgentSku
SummaryComment: A node agent SKU supported by the Batch service. The Batch node agent is a program that runs on each node in the pool, and provides the command-and-control interface between the node and the Batch service. There are different implementations of the node agent, known as SKUs, for different operating systems.

Key.Name: Id
Key.SummaryComment: The id of the node agent SKU.

Key.Name: VerifiedImageReferences
Key.SummaryComment: The list of Azure Marketplace images verified to be compatible with this node agent SKU.
Key.RemarksComment: This collection is not exhaustive (the node agent may be compatible with other images).

Key.Name: OSType
Key.SummaryComment: The type of operating system compatible with the node agent SKU.
